The Dockside Restaurant has a beautiful view of the waterfront and the ambiance was warm and contemporary.	Secondly, the room was well equipped, the decor tasteful and the bed was extremely comfortable.	The rooms are small but nice, the lobby is modern and inviting and the staff is friendly.	Otherwise, the decor and furnishings are a little tired and dated.	The hotel was well appointed, our room comfortable and decorated in a traditional style.	Generally this hotel has excellent service, is fantastic value, the restaurant is good with great views, but the best thing is that it just has a lovely relaxed and friendly atmosphere.